{"tid":131342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小學生不滿功課簿被劃花 鎅刀鎅傷同學","createTime":"2017-02-23T04:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T07:33:01.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a258d4d5fe69c38ebd511b905195fa353d9193ef","tid":131342,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:21:36.000Z","msg":"2017.02.22 21:05<br />\n<br />\n(澳門電台消息) 氹仔有小學發生傷人事件，1名學生被同學用多功能鎖匙刀鎅傷，需送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n事發於下午4時許。警方表示，事件懷疑是有人不滿功課簿被劃花引起。受傷小學生就讀小五，右大腿有3吋傷口並出血。涉事懷疑傷人學生則被警方帶返警局。(盧宇恆  鄭裕華)"},{"pid":"f836a4609e1b3f1e76ee6b66dab1a02d7abdf678","tid":131342,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"多功能鎖匙刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n澳門科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ad8b2e69adc2c0b34c2ea354c3b99ce7ba81f2","tid":131342,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:57:50.000Z","msg":"報復唔應該有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8a7e89f764d5e1377520db87f87719c190ed98","tid":131342,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"佢係合法的 係條友撩佢先"},{"pid":"59a1cf1ef6346851eb44ac84d61615a6f35be45d","tid":131342,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係合法的 係條友撩佢先</blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n做功課好大壓力"},{"pid":"560394fd739fff7de3738737194b01a5c98ab705","tid":131342,"uid":31975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"同學都係人 都會做錯嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815beed9d3d8280bacbba690b6f0f4aabb